headline: Valero Energy (VLO): A Refining Giant With Earnings Momentum and Global Reach
summary: Valero Energy Corp (NYSE:VLO) is among the best oil & gas refinery stocks to buy now. On February 13, Reuters reported that Valero Energy Corp (NYSE:VLO) was set to import up to 6.5 million barrels of crude from Venezuela in March. The report further said Valero would process the crude at its Gulf Coast refineries. […]
